➜云南彝良·郑万才咏昭通景区六首
http://www.sohu.com/a/412547928_753274	18915
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200811/1898b02689e1432f8946b7d2becf1683.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>题小草坝朝天马（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遗于此处已多时，半似脱缰半似驰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不是仙人真宝座，为何仰首向天嘶？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200811/5ea456fec8014b798281f2426c246b3d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>题大山包鸡公山（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雄踞霄中察四维，更知星月几时回。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只因有志昭天下，风雨千年亦未飞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200811/3624cb6777be491784d953e262f579c9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
